            </button>
            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>There is no fixed threshold. Pogo-sticking can happen within seconds (immediate back button from a slow or irrelevant page) or after several minutes if the content is partially relevant but ultimately fails to satisfy the query. Short dwell times under 30 seconds are commonly associated with pogo-sticking.</p></div></div>
          </div>
